table at rest. Ordinary physical activity results in fatigue, palpitation, dyspnea (shortness of breath).</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">NYHAIII<a name=\"NYHA-NYHAIII\"> </a></td><td>Marked limitation of physical activity. Comfortable at rest. Less than ordinary activity causes fatigue, palpitation, or dyspnea.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">NYHAIV<a name=\"NYHA-NYHAIV\"> </a></td><td>Unable to carry on any physical activity without discomfort. Symptoms of heart failure at rest. If any physical activity is undertaken, discomfort increases.</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
